{"title":"centos 7+ 暴露端口给外网","date":"2018-11-22T06:15:23.000Z","slug":"centos-7-暴露端口给外网","comments":true,"tags":["centOS"],"updated":"2019-05-11T13:39:03.546Z","content":"<h4 id=\"暴露端口\">暴露端口<a href=\"post/centos-7-暴露端口给外网#暴露端口\"></a></h4><ul>\n<li>firewall-cmd –zone=public –add-port=<yourip>/tcp –permanent</yourip></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"重新加载防火墙\">重新加载防火墙<a href=\"post/centos-7-暴露端口给外网#重新加载防火墙\"></a></h4><ul>\n<li>firewall-cmd –reload</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"查询是否暴露\">查询是否暴露<a href=\"post/centos-7-暴露端口给外网#查询是否暴露\"></a></h4><ul>\n<li>firewall-cmd –zone=public –query-port=<yourip>/tcp</yourip></li>\n</ul>\n","prev":{"title":"nexus3 搭建遇到的一些问题","slug":"nexus3-搭建遇到的一些问题"},"next":{"title":"Spring Cloud踩坑记录","slug":"Spring-Cloud踩坑记录"},"link":"http://wooo.io/post/centos-7-暴露端口给外网/"}